data.description: Welcome to this well-maintained single-story home with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms in the heart of Meridian. The location of this home is ideal, with close proximity to The Village, Albertsons Market Street, healthcare facilities, restaurants, and easy access to the freeway. The home features an open and bright floor plan with all new carpet throughout. The spacious kitchen is connected to the dining room and living areas. The split bedroom layout provides individual quiet space and privacy. The sale also includes the refrigerator and W/D. Moving outside, you can appreciate the covered patio and spacious yard, perfect for entertaining. The low-maintenance landscaping, complete with automatic sprinklers, makes upkeep a breeze and even includes a lawnmower. Hurry and take a look before it's gone!
